title: *PATREON PREVIEW* If You Know Me You Know Me Pt. II with Naomi Fry
description:
The OG Fuccmom continues neglecting her family behind the paywall and the meat and potatoes are heating up! Naomi and the boys are in the weeds, getting to the bottom of why she’s so beloved by the Throw Gang, seeking the validation of young people, fame vs. clout, the eternal chip on her shoulder, never looking at the numbers, who’s actually running Diplo’s Twitter, her dream interview, beefing with Jonathan Cheban, Los Angeles aka the city of dreams, the joys of parenthood, playing matchmaker for James, bits becoming bags and much more on this Patreon-exclusive romp in the mud.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
